over" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/2007/" data-brandid="2007" target="_blank">亚马逊</a>开卖<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/1459/" data-brandid="1459" target="_blank">任天堂</a>的Game&amp;Watch 35周年复刻版，好奇点进去，结果售罄，突然感觉很失落，本来并不是很想买，但瞬间激发了购买欲望。第二天惊喜地发现亚马逊又开售了，于是赶紧下单了，虽然后来又售罄，但过了一天又开售了，感觉被套路，算了，情怀无价，算是送自己的生日礼物。<span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span></p><h2 id="cl_1">外观展示</h2><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/29/5fc2ef23463c1944.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="包装非常完美"/></a>包装非常完美</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/29/5fc2ef16d4fec7356.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="很有特点的外包装"/></a>很有特点的外包装</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/29/5fc2ed81aba4a2354.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="背面介绍"/></a>背面介绍</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/29/5fc2ef059e83f4464.jpg_e