temprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/29/5fc2efc3e3a214189.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="依然没看到彩蛋"/></a>依然没看到彩蛋</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/29/5fc2f2dbc6a9f1683.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="按game键，可以选择游戏"/></a>按game键，可以选择游戏</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/29/5fc2f0207ddda8259.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="现在玩起来依然是经典！"/></a>现在玩起来依然是经典！</span></p><h2 id="cl_2">使用体验及彩蛋</h2><p itemprop="description"><a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/youxi/" target="_blank">游戏</a>是可以随时按watch键换<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/zhong/" target="_blank">时钟</a>页面，或按开机键锁屏的，游戏自动暂停，在游戏选择开始页面按住A键不放，可以调成无限命，AB键是软的，手感很好，十字键相对硬一点，但个人感觉手感还不错。</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span>每天在工作累了的时候，抽出5分钟，忙里偷闲，摸个鱼，挺好的。</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_17/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/30/5fc44798975be7802.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="时钟页面长按A，出现画马里奥之歌"/></a>时钟页面长按A，出现画马里奥之歌</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a83g2487/pic_18/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/30/5fc4479939e2f13.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="一边唱一边画"/></a>一边唱一边画</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="im